message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This item holds significant value to me due to its unique features and craftsmanship, which I believe are worth more than what others might perceive. Given its importance to my business, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $10,000. This is a special opportunity tailored for you, considering its worth to you is $8,000. I hope we can come to an agreement that benefits both of us.
